             was indicted for <rs id="t17730908-82-off370" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17730908-82-off370" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17730908-82-off370" type="offenceSubcategory" value="forgery"></interp>
               feloniously forging the last will and testament of 
                     <persName id="t17730908-82-person752">
                        Elizabeth
                         Shuter
