                        <interp inst="t17730908-82-person752" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                     </persName>
                  , spinster, with intention to defraud the 
                     <persName id="t17730908-82-victim753" type="victimName">
                        <rs id="t17730908-82-viclabel371" type="occupation">Governor and Company of Merchants of Great Britain trading to the South Seas and other parts of America, and for encouraging the fishery</rs>
